    Testing
    Packaging(jar/war file)

    //Gradle
    Gradle bhi Maven jaisa build automation tool hai, lekin ye faster hota h aur scripting based configuration use karta h.

    //Difference between Maven and Gradle

    Maven is xml based and pom.xml
    Gradle is Script based and build.gradle



